andha kanoon ( hindi : अंधा क़ानून ; english : blind law ) is a 1983 bollywood drama film directed by t. rama rao , starring rajinikanth ( who makes his bollywood debut ) , hema malini , amitabh bacchan , reena roy madhavi . it is a remake of the tamil film sattam oru iruttarai ( 1981 ) . the film also has a huge supporting cast including pran , danny denzongpa , amrish puri , madan puri , prem chopra and asrani . dharmendra also made a guest appearance .